          "supportingText": "Page 1: Standardized achievement test scores of high ability students showed a significant increase after a year of ability grouping.' ' An example was the Fort Worth Independent School District, w here high and regular ability groups were formed in all elementary schools from 1975 to 1982 at the beginning of the fourth grade."
